        "implementation",
        "state-machine",
        "startup-check",
        "camera-config",
        "plc-communication",
        "frame-processing"
      ],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "大量使用 Qt 信号槽（DirectConnection 低延迟 + QueuedConnection 跨线程），通过 std::atomic 实现无锁运行模式读写，利用 QSystemSemaphore 实现单实例锁。"
    },
